# Build artifacts -- regenerated on demand by build_pdf.py.
# The Markdown source under source/ and the style.css are the
# tracked truth.
#
# spody-user-manual.html: intermediate (browser preview only), not tracked.
# spody-user-manual.pdf : shipped inside the PyInstaller bundle via the
#   spec's 'datas' entry; we keep it tracked so bundle builds don't
#   depend on Chromium-class browser availability in CI. Rebuild with
#   `python build_pdf.py` and re-commit when the Markdown source under
#   source/ changes.
spody-user-manual.html
